#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:1
msgid "Surveys (`lu_mcp_survey`)"
msgstr "Surveys (`lu_mcp_survey`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:3
msgid "**6 tools** for Odoo survey creation and response analytics."
msgstr "Odoo 설문 생성 및 응답 분석을 위한 **6가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `survey` app."
msgstr "필수: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `survey` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools let an AI client list and read existing surveys, create new "
"surveys, add questions (9 question types), view aggregated responses, and"
" generate a survey automatically from a Knowledge article."
msgstr ""
"이 도구들을 통해 AI 클라이언트는 기존 설문을 나열 및 읽기, 새 설문 생성, 질문 추가(9가지 질문 유형), "
"집계된 응답 보기, Knowledge 아티클에서 설문을 자동으로 생성할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:17
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:19
msgid "`survey_list_surveys`"
msgstr "`survey_list_surveys`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:21
msgid "List all surveys."
msgstr "모든 설문을 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "*(없음)*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:27 ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:40
#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:54 ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:103
#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:120
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:28
msgid "*\"Show all available surveys.\"*"
msgstr "*\"사용 가능한 모든 설문을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:32
msgid "`survey_read_survey`"
msgstr "`survey_read_survey`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:34
msgid "Get full details of a survey, including its questions and options."
msgstr "질문 및 옵션을 포함한 설문의 전체 상세 정보를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`survey_id`"
msgstr "`survey_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Survey ID."
msgstr "설문 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:41
msgid "*\"Show me the questions in survey #10.\"*"
msgstr "*\"설문 #10의 질문을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:45
msgid "`survey_create_survey`"
msgstr "`survey_create_survey`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:47
msgid "Create a new survey."
msgstr "새 설문을 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`title`"
msgstr "`title`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Survey title."
msgstr "설문 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`description`"
msgstr "`description`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Survey description (Markdown)."
msgstr "설문 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:55
msgid "*\"Create a survey titled 'Employee Satisfaction Q3 2026'.\"*"
msgstr "*\"'Employee Satisfaction Q3 2026'이라는 제목의 설문을 생성하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:59
msgid "`survey_add_question`"
msgstr "`survey_add_question`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:61
msgid "Add a question to an existing survey."
msgstr "기존 설문에 질문을 추가합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Question text."
msgstr "질문 텍스트."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`question_type`"
msgstr "`question_type`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Question type (default `simple_choice`). See below."
msgstr "질문 유형(기본값 `simple_choice`). 아래 참조."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`is_required`"
msgstr "`is_required`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "boolean"
msgstr "boolean"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Whether the question is mandatory (default `false`)."
msgstr "질문이 필수인지 여부(기본값 `false`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`answers`"
msgstr "`answers`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "array of string"
msgstr "array of string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid ""
"Answer choices for `simple_choice`, `multiple_choice`, `matrix`, or "
"`scale`."
msgstr ""
"`simple_choice`, `multiple_choice`, `matrix`, 또는 `scale`의 응답 선택지."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:71
msgid "**Question types**"
msgstr "**질문 유형**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`text_box`"
msgstr "`text_box`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Long text (multi-line)"
msgstr "장문 텍스트(여러 줄)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`char_box`"
msgstr "`char_box`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Short text (single line)"
msgstr "단문 텍스트(한 줄)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`numerical_box`"
msgstr "`numerical_box`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Numeric input"
msgstr "숫자 입력"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`date`"
msgstr "`date`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Date picker"
msgstr "날짜 선택"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`datetime`"
msgstr "`datetime`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Date and time picker"
msgstr "날짜/시간 선택"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`simple_choice`"
msgstr "`simple_choice`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Single-select (radio buttons)"
msgstr "단일 선택(라디오 버튼)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`multiple_choice`"
msgstr "`multiple_choice`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Multi-select (checkboxes)"
msgstr "다중 선택(체크박스)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`matrix`"
msgstr "`matrix`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Grid of rows × columns"
msgstr "행 × 열 그리드"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`scale`"
msgstr "`scale`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Numeric scale (e.g. 1–5 rating)"
msgstr "숫자 척도(예: 1~5점 평가)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:85
msgid "**Example prompt — multiple choice**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 다중 선택**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:86
msgid ""
"*\"Add a multiple-choice question 'Which features do you use?' to survey "
"#10 with options: Chat, Workflows, Alerts, Reports.\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"'Which features do you use?' 다중 선택 질문을 설문 #10에 추가하고 옵션을 Chat, Workflows, Alerts, Reports로 설정하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:88
msgid "**Example prompt — scale**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트 — 척도**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:89
msgid "*\"Add a scale question 'How satisfied are you overall?' to survey #10.\"*"
msgstr "*\"'How satisfied are you overall?' 척도 질문을 설문 #10에 추가하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:93
msgid "`survey_get_responses`"
msgstr "`survey_get_responses`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:95
msgid "Get aggregated response analytics for a survey."
msgstr "설문의 집계된 응답 분석을 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:101
msgid "Returns total responses, completion rate, and per-question answer counts."
msgstr "총 응답 수, 완료율, 질문별 응답 수를 반환합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:104
msgid "*\"Show the responses for survey #10.\"*"
msgstr "*\"설문 #10의 응답을 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:108
msgid "`survey_generate_from_knowledge`"
msgstr "`survey_generate_from_knowledge`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:110
msgid ""
"Generate a survey automatically from a Knowledge article. The LLM (Odoo "
"AI) analyzes the article content and creates relevant questions."
msgstr ""
"Knowledge 아티클에서 설문을 자동으로 생성합니다. LLM(Odoo AI)이 아티클 내용을 분석하여 관련 질문을 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:113
msgid "Requires: Odoo `knowledge` app and an AI provider configured in Odoo."
msgstr "필수: Odoo `knowledge` 앱 및 Odoo에서 구성된 AI 공급업체."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`article_id`"
msgstr "`article_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Knowledge article ID to generate from."
msgstr "생성할 Knowledge 아티클 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "`survey_title`"
msgstr "`survey_title`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md
msgid "Title for the new survey. Defaults to the article title."
msgstr "새 설문의 제목. 기본값은 아티클 제목입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/survey.md:121
msgid ""
"*\"Generate a survey from Knowledge article #55 (Product Training "
"Guide).\"*"
msgstr ""
"*\"Knowledge 아티클 #55(Product Training Guide)에서 설문을 생성하세요.\"*"

